<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>RTSP on Shrond's Log</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/tags/rtsp/</link><description>Recent content in RTSP on Shrond's Log</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2026 工蜂</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://dasia373.github.io/tags/rtsp/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>基于 RK3588 的 IMX415 低延迟 AI 视频推流系统</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/imx415-rtsp%E4%BD%8E%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9Fai%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%8E%A8%E6%B5%81%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</link><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/imx415-rtsp%E4%BD%8E%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9Fai%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%8E%A8%E6%B5%81%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</guid><description>基于 RK3588 / IMX415 摄像头，实现 1080p@30fps RTSP 推流，并集成 person + helmet 双模型实时检测。从零调试到「稳定 30fps + 300–400ms 端到端延迟 + AI 异步推理无顿挫」的完整记录。</description></item><item><title>阶段5 — 延迟问题探索（P0–P3 优化）</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/5-%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 11:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/5-%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/</guid><description>从播放器缓冲、muxdelay、GOP、resize 多个维度探索延迟优化，综合延迟从约 1s 压到约 500ms。</description></item><item><title>阶段4 — debug 延迟逐渐增大问题</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/4-debug%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9F%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 16:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/4-debug%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9F%E9%80%90%E6%B8%90%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>定位延迟从 1s 涨到 3s 的根因：PTS 用帧计数生成导致时间线漂移。改用 steady_clock 墙钟时间生成 PTS，延迟稳定不再增长。</description></item><item><title>阶段1 — IMX415 冒烟测试 + debug 卡顿问题</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/1-imx415%E5%86%92%E7%83%9F%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95-debug%E5%8D%A1%E9%A1%BF/</link><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 21:33:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/1-imx415%E5%86%92%E7%83%9F%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95-debug%E5%8D%A1%E9%A1%BF/</guid><description>打通 IMX415 V4L2 采集 → MPP H.264 编码 → FFmpeg RTSP 推流链路，定位并修复 streamingWorker 中 sleep_for(33ms) 导致的队列积压与卡顿。</description></item></channel></rss>